data.description: Calling all dreamers! This beautiful 1.5 acre property is the perfect place to call home! You're just minutes from the Aggie Expressway and everything Montgomery has to offer. Spend your morning watching white-tailed deer in your backyard, then hit the links at nearby Tiger Woods's Bluejack National the same afternoon. Imagine ending your day on the front porch, sipping a glass of local Bernhardt Wine, while enjoying the evening sunset. The charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home is the perfect countryside escape complete with inviting living area, a *huge* kitchen, and a bright cheerful primary bedroom. Property is lightly restricted and has the option to have restrictions removed. You'll have easy access to Ren Fest every fall and a short commute to the future Lone Star-Magnolia campus. What are you waiting for?
